author: Ildefonso Ortiz
title: Coronavirus Case Estimate in Mexico Climbs 47 Percent in One Week
description: Health officials revealed a new set of figures showing a 47 percent weekly jump in the estimated number of Coronavirus cases across Mexico. The total is up from 26,500 to 55,950.
content:
